 rabbit. Peeped out. Of his door. A hunter. Alas” (Elenski paused and sneezed powerfully). “Happened to pass” (the narrator replaced his pince-nez). “And his gun. Went bang. Bang. And. The. Poor” (the syllables grew more and more stressed and spaced). “Hare. Died. There.”

The “there” fell on Peter. But all the other children crowded around Elenski, clamoring for him to be the seeker. One could hear them exclaiming: “Please, please, it will be much more fun!”

